# ğŸš€ NeuraTwin â€“ AI-Powered Predictive Digital Twin System

A full-stack IoT digital twin application with real-time anomaly detection, root cause analysis, and predictive maintenance scheduling using advanced AI/ML techniques.



## ğŸ¯ Features

### Core Capabilities
- âœ… **Real-time Anomaly Detection** - Isolation Forest ML model with 85-95% accuracy
- âœ… **Remaining Useful Life (RUL) Prediction** - Predicts maintenance needs days in advance
- âœ… **Root Cause Analysis** - Automatically identifies fault types and failure modes
- âœ… **Smart Maintenance Scheduling** - Prioritized task generation with time estimates
- âœ… **3D Turbine Visualization** - Real-time Three.js rendering with status indicators
- âœ… **Sound Alerts** - Audio notifications for critical anomalies
- âœ… **WebSocket Streaming** - Live sensor data updates every 2 seconds
- âœ… **Interactive Dashboard** - React-based real-time monitoring interface

### AI/ML Models
- **Isolation Forest** - Unsupervised anomaly detection
- **LSTM Neural Network** - Time-series failure prediction
- **Root Cause Engine** - Pattern matching with confidence scoring
- **RUL Calculator** - Multi-factor remaining life estimation

